/target
# The guest crate is excluded from the workspace and built standalone; its
# target dir also caches the downloaded wasi-sdk toolchain. Its Cargo.lock and
# the vendored pac_guest.wasm ARE tracked (reproducible guest builds).
/pac-wasm-guest/target
# CI drops pregenerated wasm2c output here for cross builds (see build.rs
# OS_PROXY_RESOLVER_PAC_GUEST_C_DIR and .github/workflows/ci.yml).
/pac-wasm-guest/generated
